Liam thought about his day. If he finishes his report on time, he will go for a run. He wished he had more free time. If he weren't so busy, he would travel the world. Yesterday, he missed an important meeting. If he had set his alarm, he would have arrived punctually. He resolved to be more organized. If he plans carefully, he will achieve his goals.
Sarah considered her options. If she accepts the job offer, she will move to a new city. She wondered about her current situation. If she were braver, she would start her own business. Last year, she had a chance to invest. If she had invested then, she would have made a significant profit by now. She decided to be proactive. If she takes risks, she will discover new opportunities.
