Sarah reflected on her career path. She could have accepted that job offer in New York years ago, but she chose to stay local. If she would have taken that risk, her life would have been very different. She sometimes thinks she should have been bolder. Still, she's happy now, even if she occasionally wonders what could have been. She should have no regrets, but pondering alternate paths is natural.
